    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. Uncertainty quantification across key input parameters (flow rate, rotational speed, blood viscosity) confirms that predicted hemolysis index values remain below the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across the input uncertainty space. The CFD model is credible for its intended use to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
